Inheritance and Expansion from LLAMA 2 Community License Agreement

This "Toro-LlaMA Community License Agreement" is based upon and extends the "LLAMA 2 Community License Agreement" as established by Meta. In developing this agreement, Torus Actions SAS acknowledges the foundational framework provided by the "LLAMA 2 Community License Agreement" and builds upon it to introduce additional terms specific to the usage and distribution of "Toro-LlaMA" and its derivative works.

Supplementary Terms and Conditions:

1. In addition to adhering to the "LLAMA 2 Community License Agreement", the following supplementary terms and conditions are applicable for the use of "Toro-LlaMA" and its derivative works:

